        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-emerald-100 p-4 rounded-full w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl">üí™</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800">Resilience</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Bouncing back from challenging situations</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-emerald-100 p-4 rounded-full w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl">üó£Ô∏è</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800">Communication</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Clear, compassionate verbal and written skills</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-emerald-100 p-4 rounded-full w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl">‚öñÔ∏è</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800">Advocacy</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mt-1">Standing up for clients and social justice</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-emerald-100 p-4 rounded-full w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
